{"tid":1515071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[防 Fake News] 好明顯 Fake News 係中共班網軍推","createTime":"2019-08-29T03:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T03:23:28.000Z","uid":81154,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a51f33bebe1c651084e3066a06f75638688c326","tid":1515071,"uid":81154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:53:54.000Z","msg":"唔好屈自己人, 推 Fake News 係網軍既預謀, 以達到以下既目的:<br />\n<br />\n(1) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>煽動我地既情緒</strong></span>, 令到我地將焦點, 精神, 心力放左係d emotional 既野上面, 直接減少左去推行動 post 既, 同討論正經 post 既時間. <br />\n<br />\n(2) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊士氣</span></strong>, 營造做咩都會比個政府/黑警食住既氣氛.<br />\n<br />\n(3) <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">製造輿論陷阱</span></strong>, 令到政府/黑警有口實話我地講大話, 使我們向國際做既文宣加陪困難. 你睇 CNN 都瀨左野, 我地再比料外國傳媒, 人地都要諗過度過.<br />\n<br />\n(4) 令到我地失去道德高地, 同埋互相指摘, 形成內耗, 搞到我地互不信任.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>咁點樣做好?</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我建議一下一些心理上既建設比大家:<br />\n<br />\n我地要知道香港人既 IQ 係高過班大陸哩好多, 連日來政府/中共愈行愈錯, 輸既就係我地既集體智慧. 請各位繼續保持落去, 做一個有智有謀, 同時擁有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公正信念</strong></span>既抗爭者. 一齊為傷者, 死者做更多, 走更遠, 一齊打到呢個 30 年前既殺人政權.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港, 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7c09b1e9ecfccfd4dc8e7786f6fd79361acf05b","tid":1515071,"uid":81154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604d837d90a9b46a59d34121679b0c180fac3050","tid":1515071,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T23:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424979cda4b5f226e19666be021be8e3d7b6488f","tid":1515071,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"